description:
(Found in Collection, 7/24/95)
Long band of beads (not a continuous circle).  Main body consists of alternating white and blue beads forming small circles.  Each end of band has three beaded tassels.  Each tassel double strand white beads joined to single blue strand, then another double white strand joined together by single strand in half circle.
medium: White beads, turquiose blue beads, white string
title: Blue and White Beaded Necklace
